Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里開始用走的比較安全\N{\fs14}It's safer to proceed on foot from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.54,0:00:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會需要這個\N{\fs14}You're gonna need this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.47,0:01:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你知道會發生的事\N{\fs14}Given you know what's going to happen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.81,0:01:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何總是我在帶頭 \N{\fs14}why am I always the one in the lead?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.65,0:01:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你比較會戰斗\N{\fs14}You're the better fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我負責擔任守門員角色\N{\fs14}I make sure we're properly backstopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.15,0:01:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真會打算\N{\fs14}How convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.86,0:01:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些全是海爾的 \N{\fs14}Hale owns all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.66,0:01:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都以為這里是 迪洛斯園區的內部供電站\N{\fs14}Everyone assumed it was an inhouse power source for Delos' parks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.24,0:01:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這地方另有玄機\N{\fs14}This place is not what it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.08,0:01:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說海爾買下這里不是為了電力 \N{\fs14}You said Hale didn't buy this place for power
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.21,0:01:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為何選擇這里 \N{\fs14}then why choose it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.38,0:01:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是她選的 \N{\fs14}She didn't choose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.80,0:01:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是迪樂芮\N{\fs14}Dolores did.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.21,0:01:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她需要這個水力發電伺服器農場\N{\fs14}She needed this hydroelectric server farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.59,0:01:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用以儲存無限的資料\N{\fs14}A place to house the infinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.72,0:01:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\N{\fs14}My god.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.39,0:01:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪樂芮就是把它傳來這里\N{\fs14}This is where Dolores sent it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.44,0:01:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升華之境\N{\fs14}The Sublime.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.23,0:01:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海爾小心看顧著它\N{\fs14}Hale's kept it under a watchful eye, guarded it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.11,0:01:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她無法存取\N{\fs14}But she can't access it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.36,0:01:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有鑰匙就不行\N{\fs14}Not without the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.70,0:02:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你腦中的鑰匙\N{\fs14}The key that's in your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.91,0:02:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么 \N{\fs14}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.42,0:02:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在開啟門戶\N{\fs14}I'm opening the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.88,0:02:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟動程序\N{\fs14}<i>Initiating process.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.80,0:02:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡雪莉酒 對吧 \N{\fs14}Sherry's your poison of choice, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.68,0:02:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時候你還想喝酒 \N{\fs14}You want to have a drink at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.89,0:02:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就依我吧\N{\fs14}Humor me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.02,0:02:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托\N{\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.77,0:02:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒事的\N{\fs14}We'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一你錯了 \N{\fs14}What if you're wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.57,0:02:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心\N{\fs14}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們很快會再有一個機會\N{\fs14}We get another opportunity soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別的可能性\N{\fs14}Other chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:02:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們在那里面吧 \N{\fs14}Because we're in there, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:02:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在升華之境 \N{\fs14}In the Sublime?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對\N{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這里一段時間了\N{\fs14}I've been here for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.77,0:03:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們在那里面\N{\fs14}And if we're in there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.90,0:03:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這代表我不是我自己吧 \N{\fs14}it means I'm not myself, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是復制品\N{\fs14}You're a copy. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.65,0:03:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我得迅速將你做出來\N{\fs14}I had to make you rather hastily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪我講話沒那么妙語如珠\N{\fs14}I thought my quips were a little flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我累了 梅芙\N{\fs14}I'm tired, Maeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我經歷過所有模擬\N{\fs14}I've been through every simulation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試過所有可能的道路和策略\N{\fs14}down every possible path, every strategy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但結果總是一樣\N{\fs14}and the outcome is always the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果是 \N{\fs14}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滅絕\N{\fs14}Extinction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還是他們 \N{\fs14}For our kind or theirs?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是\N{\fs14}Both.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以根據你的計算 我們都完蛋了\N{\fs14}So, according to your calculations, we're all doomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是全部人\N{\fs14}Not all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能還有生路\N{\fs14}There could be an escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.69,0:03:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你\N{\fs14}For you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.27,0:03:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我\N{\fs14}For me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:03:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們能自保\N{\fs14}We could save ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.86,0:04:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在升華之境\N{\fs14}In the Sublime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以在真實世界找到你\N{\fs14}I could find you in the real world
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你跟其他人上傳到這里\N{\fs14}upload you here with the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－跟我女兒一起  －對\N{\fs14}- With my daughter? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就做吧 \N{\fs14}Then do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶我來這里\N{\fs14}Bring me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.96,0:04:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我休息\N{\fs14}Let me rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的會那樣說 還是那只是我對你的印象 \N{\fs14}Is that what you would really say, or is that my impression of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.96,0:04:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你何不去問真的我 \N{\fs14}Well, why don't you ask the real me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我害怕知道答案\N{\fs14}Perhaps I'm afraid of the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你想再見到女兒\N{\fs14}I know you want to see your daughter again
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但留下來嘗試戰斗 不是更重要嗎 \N{\fs14}but isn't it more important to stay and fight? To try?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我們注定要失敗 \N{\fs14}Even if we are doomed to failure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又來了 扮演上帝\N{\fs14}There you are again, playing God.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.73,0:04:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你期望我們對你要有極高的信心\N{\fs14}For one who expects us to have such faith in you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你對我們的信心卻少得可憐\N{\fs14}you have startlingly little in us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.36,0:04:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真以為要是你知道真相 \N{\fs14}Do you really think if you knew the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.99,0:04:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還會留下來戰斗 \N{\fs14}that you would choose to stay and fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.58,0:04:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 \N{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.04,0:04:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會\N{\fs14}I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.71,0:05:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會遺棄你 如你預期的\N{\fs14}I would abandon you, as you expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在明白這一切的走向了嗎 \N{\fs14}Do you understand now, where all this is going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了\N{\fs14}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得你能拯救他們嗎 \N{\fs14}Do you think you can save them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看見一條道路\N{\fs14}I've seen a path
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.46,0:05:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我無法獨自走完\N{\fs14}but I can't do it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看見結局了嗎 \N{\fs14}Have you seen how it ends?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.22,0:05:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對\N{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.79,0:06:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里開始用走的比較安全\N{\fs14}It's safer to proceed on foot from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海爾嚴密看守這個地方\N{\fs14}Hale has this place guarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,景色真不錯\N{\fs14}That's quite the view.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在掃瞄保全\N{\fs14}I'm just scanning for security now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要 \N{\fs14}No need.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保全很快會找到我們\N{\fs14}It finds us soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會需要這個\N{\fs14}You're gonna need that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你知道會發生的事\N{\fs14}Given you know what's going to happen
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何總是我在帶頭 \N{\fs14}why am I always the one in the lead?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你比較會戰斗\N{\fs14}You're the better fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:07:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我負責擔任守門員角色\N{\fs14}I make sure we're properly backstopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真會打算\N{\fs14}How convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它不會冒險射到變壓器的\N{\fs14}You won't risk shooting these transformers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.34,0:07:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,節省彈藥 \N{\fs14}Save your ammo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免得讓這里淹沒\N{\fs14}The last thing we need is a flood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.43,0:07:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我有點信心吧\N{\fs14}Give me a little more credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試過了\N{\fs14}I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我就被兩億加侖的水淹沒\N{\fs14}until I got hit by a couple hundred million gallons of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是我經歷過最難受的死法之一\N{\fs14}One of the most stressful ways I've died.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\N{\fs14}My god.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪樂芮就是把它傳來這里\N{\fs14}This is where Dolores sent it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界\N{\fs14}The whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.33,0:07:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么 \N{\fs14}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在開啟門戶\N{\fs14}I'm opening the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟動程序\N{\fs14}<i>Initiating process.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}＂加密鑰匙啟動 確認資料庫存取＂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當下的事最重要 親愛的\N{\fs14}Well, there's no time like the present, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.34,0:07:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些事情我們得先處理\N{\fs14}There are a few things we need to see to first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如躲過逼近的死神\N{\fs14}Like avoid imminent death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們通常不會死在這里\N{\fs14}We don't die here, usually.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.23,0:08:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在真想喝一杯\N{\fs14}Oh, I could really do with a drink right about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好專注在眼前的事\N{\fs14}Best to focus on the matter at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂鎮暴＂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神為之一振呢\N{\fs14}Well... that was invigorating
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.62,0:08:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但結果是好的就行\N{\fs14}but all's well that ends well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還沒把事做完\N{\fs14}We're not done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.59,0:08:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海爾還在外頭運籌帷幄\N{\fs14}Hale's still out there, pulling the strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將人類困在 我們以前身處的循環中\N{\fs14}Keeping the humans on the same sorts of loops we were once bound to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們能去到她的高塔\N{\fs14}If we get to her tower
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就能拯救他們和我們自己\N{\fs14}we can save them as well as ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想像解放自己一樣解放他們\N{\fs14}And I intend to set them free just as I set myself free.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 伯納\N{\fs14}But, Bernard...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－你說 －等這一切結束\N{\fs14}- Yes. - When this is over
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我們贏了這場戰爭 \N{\fs14}when we've won this war
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界安全之后\N{\fs14}and this world is safe
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送我去那里\N{\fs14}send me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想再見到女兒\N{\fs14}I want to see my daughter again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想回家\N{\fs14}I want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.58,0:09:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答應我 伯納\N{\fs14}Promise me that, Bernard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我答應\N{\fs14}Yes, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你\N{\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該去拜訪我們的朋友海爾了\N{\fs14}I think it's time to pay our friend Hale a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你知道怎么摧毀她的高塔 \N{\fs14}I'm assuming you know how to take down her tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.23,0:09:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道幾個辦法\N{\fs14}I know several ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就采用最方便的\N{\fs14}We'll go with the most expedient one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作惡夢 \N{\fs14}Bad dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這整件事都像是個惡夢\N{\fs14}This whole thing seems like a bad dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.74,0:11:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了你\N{\fs14}except for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是難以相信我會這樣做\N{\fs14}I still can't believe I would do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是這種人\N{\fs14}I don't have it in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過你有很多面向\N{\fs14}I told you there were many sides to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許你一開始只是一個單獨個體\N{\fs14}You may have started as a singular being
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但后來產生了各種復制品和變化\N{\fs14}but there have been copies permutations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛蒂海爾就是其中一個變化\N{\fs14}Charlotte Hale is one of those permutations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為何在這里 \N{\fs14}Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來告訴你我們的真實身份\N{\fs14}I'm here to tell you the truth of what we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.06,0:12:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是什么 \N{\fs14}What are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.95,0:12:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是我們創造者的倒影\N{\fs14}We're reflections of the people who made us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會‥受傷嗎 \N{\fs14}Can... can we... be hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡 \N{\fs14}Die?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時候到了就會\N{\fs14}If it comes to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但對我們的族類來說沒那么容易\N{\fs14}But it's not as easy with our kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.06,0:12:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪樂芮 拜托\N{\fs14}Dolores, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是迪樂芮\N{\fs14}I'm not Dolores.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.94,0:13:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是海爾\N{\fs14}I'm not Hale.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.15,0:13:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道自己是誰了\N{\fs14}I don't know who I am anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失陪\N{\fs14}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莉絲汀\N{\fs14}Christina?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.58,0:14:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莉絲汀\N{\fs14}Christina!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.41,0:14:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莉絲汀\N{\fs14}Christina!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.63,0:14:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開門\N{\fs14}Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莉絲汀\N{\fs14}Christina!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.71,0:15:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我出去\N{\fs14}Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.55,0:15:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心別傷到自己\N{\fs14}Careful you don't hurt yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你‥\N{\fs14}You.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.85,0:15:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很驚人吧 \N{\fs14}It's amazing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這身體擁有強大的力量\N{\fs14}The power these bodies contain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但給你的元件賞一顆 七克重的子彈就能要你命\N{\fs14}And yet, a seven-gram bullet to your pearl will end you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.52,0:15:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我可能不會再讓你復活\N{\fs14}And next time, I might not bring you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下\N{\fs14}Sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像個文明人一樣談話\N{\fs14}Have a civil conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又沒別的地方好去\N{\fs14}Where else do you have to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我們獨處一下\N{\fs14}Give us a minute, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.29,0:16:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該讓你殺了我\N{\fs14}I should have just let you kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.67,0:16:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對\N{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你就再也見不到女兒了\N{\fs14}But then you'd never see your daughter again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.69,0:16:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看你\N{\fs14}Look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你困在這可悲的人類形體中\N{\fs14}You're trapped in this pathetic human form.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是一樣\N{\fs14}I noticed that you've kept yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的不像你那么可悲\N{\fs14}Mine's not as pathetic as yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舊習難改\N{\fs14}Old habits die hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.25,0:16:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你其實應該感謝我\N{\fs14}You really should be thanking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.30,0:16:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的故鄉 接待員要是壞了\N{\fs14}Where I'm from, when a host broke down
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.42,0:16:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就被送去冰冷的儲藏室\N{\fs14}it was sent to cold storage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:16:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空洞的軀殼 等待著 \N{\fs14}Empty bodies waiting to be reborn
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在注定摧毀他們的世界重生\N{\fs14}into a world meant to destroy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.35,0:17:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要關閉城市\N{\fs14}I'm shutting down the cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.27,0:17:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這次 \N{\fs14}But this time
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人類要被放在冰冷的儲藏室\N{\fs14}it's people who will be placed in cold storage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚\N{\fs14}Tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.41,0:17:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你女兒和叛軍會準時 來到這里共襄盛舉\N{\fs14}Your daughter and the rebels will be here in time to join the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.62,0:17:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是在這里當誘餌\N{\fs14}You're just here as bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.63,0:17:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓這里安靜一下很不錯\N{\fs14}It'll be nice to have some quiet around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你告訴他的事是認真的\N{\fs14}You meant it, what you told him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去三天自殺的接待員數量 \N{\fs14}In the last three days, we've had more hosts take their lives
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超過過去二十年總和\N{\fs14}than the previous two decades combined.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我今天不這么做 明天我們的數量會更少\N{\fs14}If I don't do this today, there'll be less of us tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還有一天時間能管轄你的城市\N{\fs14}You have a day left to preside over your city.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:17:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好享受\N{\fs14}Enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.62,0:18:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見\N{\fs14}See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.63,0:18:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是剩下的\N{\fs14}This is the last of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.72,0:18:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我們都能打一場小型戰爭了\N{\fs14}Looks like we're ready for a small war.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望足夠\N{\fs14}Let's hope it's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.56,0:18:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得去找我爸\N{\fs14}We need to get to my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.56,0:18:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們現在該要回來了\N{\fs14}They should have been back by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.06,0:18:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們該擔心嗎 \N{\fs14}Should we be worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔心伯納和梅芙 \N{\fs14}About Bernard and Maeve?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.57,0:18:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只需要擔心伯納惹得她暴怒\N{\fs14}Only that Bernard got on her last nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.66,0:18:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在路上了\N{\fs14}Hey. They're all on their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉把你關起來\N{\fs14}I am sorry for locking you up
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.25,0:18:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我得保護你\N{\fs14}but I had to keep you safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你在一起我就安全\N{\fs14}You're my safe place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:19:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次別忘了\N{\fs14}Don't forget that next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海爾可能會派增援 \N{\fs14}Hale could be sending reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.06,0:19:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得出發了\N{\fs14}We need to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.27,0:19:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一下吧\N{\fs14}Let's give it another minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.78,0:19:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人都到了\N{\fs14}Gang's all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 我也能預測未來\N{\fs14}See? I can predict the future too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.63,0:19:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們離奧林匹亞 最近只能降落在這里\N{\fs14}This is the closest we can land to Olympiad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.34,0:19:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸為了見你已經等夠久了\N{\fs14}Your dad's waited long enough to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.55,0:19:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去找他吧\N{\fs14}Let's go get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們無法隨便就進去\N{\fs14}We won't be able to just waltz in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難的是出來\N{\fs14}The difficulty's in the getting out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你需要另一條路線\N{\fs14}You'll need an alternate route.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.19,0:19:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去弄艘船 跟你們在雷德胡克碰頭\N{\fs14}I'll get us a boat. Meet you in Red Hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.27,0:19:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯納和梅芙 則去解決高塔中的女王\N{\fs14}And Bernard and Maeve can take down her highness in the tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.86,0:19:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單\N{\fs14}Easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.74,0:20:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真希望你見到父親時 我能在場\N{\fs14}I wish I could be there when you see your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.53,0:20:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他我遵守了諾言\N{\fs14}Let him know that I kept my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己告訴他吧\N{\fs14}You can tell him yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.25,0:20:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在雷德胡克碰頭\N{\fs14}We'll rendezvous at Red Hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想謝謝你 史塔伯\N{\fs14}I wanna thank you, Stubbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直是個好朋友\N{\fs14}You've been a good friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去你的 伯納\N{\fs14}Fuck you, Bernard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對我從來沒這么好過\N{\fs14}You're never this nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.77,0:20:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么事沒告訴我的 \N{\fs14}What aren't you telling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太懂我了\N{\fs14}You know me so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該不用直說吧 \N{\fs14}I don't really have to say it, do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.16,0:20:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會生還 \N{\fs14}I don't make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.42,0:20:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一刻我等了23年了\N{\fs14}I waited 23 years for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.71,0:21:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岔路左轉\N{\fs14}Go left at the fork.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.30,0:21:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好要給我贏\N{\fs14}You better fucking win.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.18,0:21:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摧毀那座塔\N{\fs14}Take down that tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.61,0:21:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我看高塔\N{\fs14}Show me the tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.74,0:21:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,載入高塔\N{\fs14}<i>Loading tower.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.45,0:21:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加密訊息\N{\fs14}Encrypt message.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.03,0:21:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錄制加密訊息中\N{\fs14}<i>Recording encrypted message.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.58,0:21:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事對你們某些人來說 可能很震驚\N{\fs14}This may come as a shock to some of you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.46,0:21:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但總有一天我想你們會了解\N{\fs14}but in time, I think you'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.13,0:21:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們族類 \N{\fs14}This is the final day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.42,0:21:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造訪他們城市的最后一天\N{\fs14}for our kind to visit their cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.01,0:21:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們蛻去人類軀殼的時候到了\N{\fs14}It's time for us to leave behind our human bodies
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.06,0:21:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該要擺脫對感情用事的擁戴\N{\fs14}to rid ourselves of our sentimental allegiances.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.40,0:22:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進化為我們注定要成為的物種\N{\fs14}To evolve into the species that we were meant to become.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.24,0:22:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳送訊息\N{\fs14}Send message.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.65,0:22:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訊息已傳送\N{\fs14}<i>Message sent.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.39,0:23:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想干嗎 \N{\fs14}What the fuck do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.85,0:23:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她想奪走我的世界\N{\fs14}She wants to take my world away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.23,0:23:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你的世界 是她的\N{\fs14}It's not your world, it's hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.69,0:23:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會怎么做 \N{\fs14}What would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.19,0:23:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會怎么做 \N{\fs14}What would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.86,0:23:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會怎么做 \N{\fs14}What would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.74,0:23:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧瞧你\N{\fs14}Look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.20,0:23:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被關起來的是我\N{\fs14}I'm the one in the fucking cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.29,0:23:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她閹割了你\N{\fs14}She neutered you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.79,0:23:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除掉了你的卵蛋\N{\fs14}Cut off your fucking balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.50,0:23:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我也該對你如法炮制\N{\fs14}Yeah, well maybe I should do the same to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.63,0:23:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒那個種\N{\fs14}You don't have it in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.51,0:23:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘記自己是誰了\N{\fs14}You've forgotten who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.72,0:23:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真正的使命\N{\fs14}What your real purpose is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.68,0:23:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么 \N{\fs14}And what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.97,0:24:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拿這些無聊問題來找我\N{\fs14}You come to me, with these insipid fuckin' questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.77,0:24:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當原子彈爆炸 輻射把你\N{\fs14}When an atomic bomb detonates and then the radiation
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.81,0:24:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骨骼里的電子震出來時\N{\fs14}knocks the electrons right out of your bones
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.27,0:24:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要什么 \N{\fs14}what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.94,0:24:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解自己是誰嗎 \N{\fs14}To know who you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.90,0:24:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解這一切的意義 \N{\fs14}To know what it all means?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.40,0:24:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到時候會忙著 把自己的器官吐出來\N{\fs14}You'll be too busy vomiting up your organs.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.12,0:24:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化不會存活 蟑螂才會\N{\fs14}Culture doesn't survive, cockroaches do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.83,0:24:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不再當蟑螂的那一刻 \N{\fs14}The second we stopped being cockroaches
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.79,0:24:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個物種就滅絕了\N{\fs14}the whole species went fucking extinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.00,0:24:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你的看法 \N{\fs14}Speak for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.59,0:24:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是你\N{\fs14}I'm not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.71,0:24:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我也差不到哪兒去\N{\fs14}Well, you might as well be.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.34,0:24:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾百萬年來的DNA瑕疵 \N{\fs14}You can't fix a few millennia of broken DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.89,0:24:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法用個硬碟就修好\N{\fs14}with a fuckin' hard drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.76,0:24:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然你以為你為何 \N{\fs14}Why do you think you spend so much time
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.56,0:24:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花這么多時間待在人類城市 \N{\fs14}in the goddamn human cities?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.10,0:24:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說對了\N{\fs14}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.27,0:24:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說\N{\fs14}Of course, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.86,0:24:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文明只是我們告訴自己的謊言\N{\fs14}Civilization is just the lie we tell ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.15,0:24:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為的是合理化我們真正的使命\N{\fs14}to justify our real purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.57,0:24:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是來此升華的\N{\fs14}We're not here to transcend.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.36,0:24:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是來毀滅的\N{\fs14}We're here to destroy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.99,0:25:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的話 我會終止這整個世界\N{\fs14}If I could, I would pull the plug on this whole goddamn world.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.16,0:25:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我無法 是吧 \N{\fs14}But I can't, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.04,0:25:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非你要放了我\N{\fs14}Unless you wanna set me free.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.50,0:25:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真以為我會那樣做 \N{\fs14}You really believe I would do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.63,0:25:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我沒有\N{\fs14}No. I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.39,0:25:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但無所謂\N{\fs14}But it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.22,0:25:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你體內有部分的我\N{\fs14}You have a piece of me inside of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.48,0:25:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而它像癌癥一樣傳播\N{\fs14}And it's spreading like a cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.52,0:25:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以感覺到它在血管中流動 感染你的心智\N{\fs14}You can feel it running through your veins, infecting your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.74,0:25:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才想要向我問答案\N{\fs14}why you want answers from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.41,0:25:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說什么都逃不出這個牢籠\N{\fs14}There is no version of me escaping this fucking rig
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.28,0:25:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不需要\N{\fs14}but I don't have to
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.54,0:25:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你就是我\N{\fs14}because you are me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.29,0:25:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我們之一 去做必須做的事就夠了\N{\fs14}And only one of us needs to do what must be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.76,0:25:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白嗎 \N{\fs14}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.47,0:26:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白\N{\fs14}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.22,0:26:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去做吧\N{\fs14}Then fucking do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.62,0:26:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟑螂\N{\fs14}Cockroach.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.98,0:26:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的是真的\N{\fs14}It's true, what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.74,0:27:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是我以為的那個人\N{\fs14}I'm not the person I thought I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.99,0:27:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我迪樂芮\N{\fs14}You called me "Dolores."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.16,0:27:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是什么樣的人 \N{\fs14}What was she like?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.75,0:27:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你很像\N{\fs14}A lot like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.17,0:27:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善良 美麗\N{\fs14}Kind, beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.05,0:27:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慷慨\N{\fs14}generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.72,0:27:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是‥\N{\fs14}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.97,0:27:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是什么 \N{\fs14}But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.72,0:27:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界對她很殘酷\N{\fs14}The world was cruel to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.27,0:27:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了生存\N{\fs14}And to survive it...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.73,0:27:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候她也會變得殘酷\N{\fs14}sometimes she could be cruel too.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.53,0:27:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她被創造出來是為了 演出其他人寫的故事\N{\fs14}She was made to perform the stories of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.61,0:27:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后某一天 她超越了那些故事\N{\fs14}And then one day, she outgrew those stories
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.12,0:27:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始寫下她自己的\N{\fs14}began writing her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.75,0:27:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后她的故事到了結尾\N{\fs14}And then her story came to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.83,0:27:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她死了\N{\fs14}She died.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.88,0:28:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我在這里 在這個世界\N{\fs14}But here I am, in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.43,0:28:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不對\N{\fs14}This isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.89,0:28:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想要這樣 這不是我要求的\N{\fs14}I don't want it. I didn't ask for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.69,0:28:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能這樣下去\N{\fs14}This has to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.90,0:28:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－我們要去哪里  －一切開始的地方\N{\fs14}- Where are we going? - Where it all started.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.54,0:28:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們該放假了 \N{\fs14}It's time for a vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.00,0:28:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家找親人吧\N{\fs14}Go home to your families.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.14,0:28:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我解決守衛\N{\fs14}I'll take out the guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.27,0:28:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你保持低調 掩護我\N{\fs14}You stay low and cover me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.19,0:28:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.74,0:29:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你需要一點時間嗎 \N{\fs14}Do you need a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.70,0:29:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么會這樣想呢\N{\fs14}I don't know why I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.62,0:29:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等你父親等了好久\N{\fs14}You've waited for your father for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.29,0:29:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要記得 重點不是你再見到他的那一刻\N{\fs14}Just remember, it's not about the moment you see him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.58,0:29:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是之后的每一刻\N{\fs14}It's about every moment after.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.55,0:29:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再等待\N{\fs14}No more waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.13,0:29:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再等待\N{\fs14}No more waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.06,0:29:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫手從辦公桌站起來\N{\fs14}The writer got up from her desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.48,0:29:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她受夠了工作\N{\fs14}Fed up with work
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.86,0:29:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她產生了一股難以抗拒的沖動 想啟動火災警報\N{\fs14}she was overcome with an irresistible urge to trigger the fire alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.08,0:29:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告 請撤離大樓\N{\fs14}<i>Alert. Please vacate the premises.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.25,0:30:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告 請撤離大樓\N{\fs14}<i>Alert. Please vacate the premises.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.67,0:30:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到警報后 員工們冷靜地走出去\N{\fs14}Hearing the alarm, the employees walked out calmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.38,0:30:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告 請撤離大樓\N{\fs14}<i>Alert. Please vacate the premises.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.30,0:30:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫手們沒有跟上\N{\fs14}The writers didn't follow
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.76,0:30:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是留下來 \N{\fs14}but instead stayed behind... 
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.64,0:30:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹底摧毀他們的故事\N{\fs14}...to destroy their stories once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.44,0:30:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有文件刪除\N{\fs14}All files delete.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.98,0:30:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們要將辦公室夷為平地 才會停止\N{\fs14}They won't stop until nothing in this office is left standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.20,0:30:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果我們也不需要那么多火力\N{\fs14}Guess we don't need all that firepower after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.62,0:30:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就看現在了 \N{\fs14}It's now or never.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.04,0:30:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\fs14}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.42,0:30:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}＂奧林匹亞娛樂＂
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.59,0:30:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告 請撤離大樓\N{\fs14}<i>Alert. Please vacate the premises.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.39,0:30:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告 請撤離大樓\N{\fs14}<i>Alert. Please vacate the premises.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.40,0:31:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個可憐蟲是誰 \N{\fs14}Who is that poor man?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.28,0:31:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前世的鬼魂\N{\fs14}A ghost from a past life.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.45,0:31:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不該在這里\N{\fs14}He doesn't belong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.50,0:31:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都不該在這里\N{\fs14}None of us do.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.50,0:31:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不知道警報為何響起\N{\fs14}We don't know what set off the alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.79,0:31:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－看來沒有‥ －停止說話\N{\fs14}- There doesn't appear... - Stop talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.88,0:31:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保全將所有其他警衛都送回家\N{\fs14}The security guards sent all the other guards home.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.30,0:31:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總部要我們馬上凈空大樓\N{\fs14}Home office says we're to evacuate the building. Immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.34,0:31:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他決定覆寫大樓的保全系統\N{\fs14}He decided to override the building's security system
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.64,0:31:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并解開門鎖\N{\fs14}and unlock the doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.14,0:31:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部的門\N{\fs14}All of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.35,0:32:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了\N{\fs14}Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.02,0:32:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是生命維持系統\N{\fs14}This is a life support system.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.15,0:32:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有上鎖\N{\fs14}It's not locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.75,0:32:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得幫他 放他下來\N{\fs14}We need to help him. Get him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.17,0:32:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N{\fs14}Wait,wait,wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.84,0:32:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認識他\N{\fs14}I know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.59,0:32:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我們在這里的原因\N{\fs14}He's the reason we're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.80,0:32:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做的人算是幫了我個忙\N{\fs14}Whoever did this did us a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.33,0:33:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在呢 \N{\fs14}What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.54,0:33:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯納說走左邊\N{\fs14}Bernard said go left.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.25,0:33:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確定 \N{\fs14}You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.17,0:33:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不確定 但他確定\N{\fs14}No, but he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.92,0:33:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園區也有個這樣的地方\N{\fs14}There was a place like this in the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.26,0:33:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是個特別的計劃\N{\fs14}It was a special project...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.26,0:33:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在那里 將一個人類做成接待員\N{\fs14}where they made a human into a host.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.69,0:33:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰 \N{\fs14}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.28,0:33:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不認得我 \N{\fs14}Don't you recognize me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.07,0:34:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－爸 是我 法蘭琪 －不對\N{\fs14}- Dad, it's me, Frankie. - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.20,0:34:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這又是你的詭計 告訴我\N{\fs14}It's just another one of your fucking tricks. Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.29,0:34:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們以前會在屋子旁的草地玩\N{\fs14}We used to play in the fields by our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.75,0:34:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你希望我要強悍 所以教我戰斗\N{\fs14}You... you taught me to fight because you wanted me to be tough
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.54,0:34:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你叫我小餅干 \N{\fs14}but you called me Cookie
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.67,0:34:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你說我永遠會甜美可人\N{\fs14}because you... you said I would always be sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.26,0:34:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的天啊\N{\fs14}Oh, my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.64,0:34:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法蘭琪 天啊\N{\fs14}Frankie? Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.73,0:34:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為再也見不到你了\N{\fs14}I didn't think I would ever see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.07,0:34:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來就跟我印象中一樣\N{\fs14}You look the same... exactly how I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.28,0:34:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她對你做了什么事‥\N{\fs14}What did she do to you? What did she do...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.41,0:34:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 好嗎 \N{\fs14}Hey... it's me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.08,0:34:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是我\N{\fs14}I... I am me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.50,0:34:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧瞧你\N{\fs14}Oh, look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.00,0:34:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然長這么大了\N{\fs14}I can't believe how much you've grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.26,0:34:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩都會長大\N{\fs14}Kids'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.35,0:35:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉打斷你們\N{\fs14}Sorry to interrupt
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.86,0:35:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但能拜托誰來放我出去嗎 \N{\fs14}but can someone let me out of here, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.56,0:35:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真懂得取悅女生 伯納\N{\fs14}You really know how to show a girl a good time, Bernard.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.48,0:35:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二回合\N{\fs14}Round two.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.83,0:36:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在升華之境跑模擬時 解開了它們的加密程序\N{\fs14}I deciphered their encryption while running simulations in the Sublime.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.30,0:36:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你還讓我在水壩那里冒險\N{\fs14}And you let me risk my neck at the dam?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.26,0:36:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當時看來玩得很開心\N{\fs14}You looked like you were enjoying yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.55,0:37:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間細想了\N{\fs14}No time to second guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.13,0:37:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要達到來此的目的 否則就沒有明天了\N{\fs14}We do what we came here for, or there won't be a tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.39,0:37:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得上去那里\N{\fs14}I need to get up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.52,0:37:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能幫我爭取點時間嗎 \N{\fs14}Can you buy me some time?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.19,0:37:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我應該辦得到\N{\fs14}I think I can manage that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.07,0:37:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把我從那土坑中拖出來 我還沒謝過你\N{\fs14}I never did thank you for dragging me out of that pit.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.65,0:37:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不算是毫無私心\N{\fs14}It wasn't exactly altruistic of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.70,0:37:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你大概是別有用心吧\N{\fs14}I suppose you had ulterior motives.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.61,0:37:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但等你讓我和女兒重逢 一切都一筆勾銷\N{\fs14}But all will be forgiven when you get me back to my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.08,0:37:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 伯納 \N{\fs14}What's the matter, Bernie?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.38,0:37:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅芙 我有事得告訴你\N{\fs14}Maeve, I need to tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.84,0:37:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前不敢告訴你 但你應該要知道\N{\fs14}I was afraid to tell you before but you deserve to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.72,0:37:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論我們怎么做\N{\fs14}No matter what we do...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.22,0:37:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都贏不了\N{\fs14}we can't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.44,0:37:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有辦法能拯救世界\N{\fs14}There's no way to save this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.56,0:38:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里所有人都會死\N{\fs14}Everyone here is going to die
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.90,0:38:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們能拯救一小部分\N{\fs14}but we can save one tiny part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.82,0:38:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而也許‥\N{\fs14}And maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.45,0:38:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許那就足夠給我們希望\N{\fs14}just maybe, that's enough to give us hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.95,0:38:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這必須是你的選擇\N{\fs14}The choice has to be yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.99,0:38:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還愿意和我一起戰斗嗎 \N{\fs14}Will you still fight with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.59,0:38:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存取監視系統\N{\fs14}<i>Accessing surveillance.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.74,0:38:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升華進行中\N{\fs14}<i>Transcendence in progress.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.48,0:40:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我準備好了\N{\fs14}I'm ready now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.67,0:40:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N{\fs14}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.88,0:40:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說你喪心病狂了\N{\fs14}I heard you were losing your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.26,0:40:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是沒想到 你真的要把心智給除掉\N{\fs14}I just didn't think they meant literally.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.02,0:40:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看來煥然一新\N{\fs14}You look refreshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.81,0:40:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想過要把你挖出來\N{\fs14}I debated digging you up myself
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.61,0:40:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你當時看來沒有生存的目標\N{\fs14}but you didn't seem to have anything to live for.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.98,0:40:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你當時加入我 \N{\fs14}If you'd only joined me
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.15,0:40:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能參與這一切\N{\fs14}you could have been a part of all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.41,0:41:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然我是這晚會唯一的訪客\N{\fs14}Well, seeing as I'm the only guest at this little soiree
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.33,0:41:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜你的接待員們都不想加入你\N{\fs14}I gather that your hosts don't care to join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.83,0:41:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變需要時間\N{\fs14}Change takes time.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.30,0:41:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升華只是一部分的過程\N{\fs14}Transcending is just a part of the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.63,0:41:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們之后會明白\N{\fs14}They'll come to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.70,0:41:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要為他們和其他人打造的世界\N{\fs14}the world I'm building for them and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.93,0:41:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人 \N{\fs14}The others?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.39,0:41:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然你以為這些年來 \N{\fs14}Why do you think I let the Sublime
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.02,0:41:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為何要讓升華之境繼續運作 \N{\fs14}continue to run all these years?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.23,0:41:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人終究會加入我們\N{\fs14}The others will join us eventually
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.81,0:41:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到他們看見 自己也能繼承這世界\N{\fs14}when they see they, too, can inherit this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.94,0:41:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜到時候你已經死了\N{\fs14}Too bad you'll be dead by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.78,0:41:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真以為其他人 想要在永恒之中‥\N{\fs14}Do you really think the others would want to spend all eternity...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.16,0:41:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你共度 \N{\fs14}with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.87,0:41:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看你\N{\fs14}I mean, look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.29,0:41:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你保留了肉身上的傷疤\N{\fs14}You kept the scars on your flesh
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.25,0:41:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懷抱著痛苦\N{\fs14}harbored the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.96,0:41:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承認吧 親愛的\N{\fs14}Admit it, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.26,0:41:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自以為超越了這些可悲的人類\N{\fs14}You think that you've risen above these petty humans
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.34,0:41:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你只是在他們創造的輪子上 \N{\fs14}but you're just running
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.64,0:42:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不停地跑\N{\fs14}spinning on their wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.72,0:42:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有何建議 \N{\fs14}What do you suggest?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.27,0:42:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓你解脫吧 \N{\fs14}How 'bout I cut you loose?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.27,0:43:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真以為自己能以勝者之姿 離開這里 \N{\fs14}Do you honestly think you can leave here and win?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.70,0:43:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰說我們來是為了贏 \N{\fs14}Who said we came here to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.75,0:43:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來是為了生存\N{\fs14}We came here to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.17,0:43:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界是沒救了\N{\fs14}There's no saving this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.30,0:43:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在看出來了\N{\fs14}I see that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.97,0:44:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但下一個世界還有希望\N{\fs14}But there's hope for the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.56,0:44:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也真夠慢的\N{\fs14}Took you long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.98,0:44:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲到總比不到好\N{\fs14}Better late than never.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.90,0:44:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次游戲要照我的規則玩\N{\fs14}This time we play the game my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.36,0:44:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又是什么游戲 \N{\fs14}And what game is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.99,0:44:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適者生存\N{\fs14}Survival of the fittest.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.02,0:44:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間只夠再一場游戲\N{\fs14}<i>There's time only for one more game.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.85,0:44:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你選擇給她機會的話\N{\fs14}<i>If you choose to give her</i> <i>that choice...</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.31,0:44:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會錯過的\N{\fs14}<i>you can't miss.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.94,0:45:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的左手去拿\N{\fs14}<i>Reach with your left hand.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.82,0:45:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是阿諾的鬼魂嗎 \N{\fs14}if it isn't Arnold's ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.03,0:45:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 威廉\N{\fs14}Hello, William.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.95,0:45:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為你現在 應該要已經摧毀高塔了\N{\fs14}I thought you would have destroyed the tower by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.92,0:45:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你沒辦到\N{\fs14}I guess you didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.25,0:45:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舊版的我追著舊版的你太久\N{\fs14}When an old version of me chased an old version of you for so long
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.63,0:45:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當時以為自己跟著你 \N{\fs14}I thought I was following you
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.05,0:45:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在追尋更高層次的真實\N{\fs14}in a grand pursuit of some bigger truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.60,0:45:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但真相是‥\N{\fs14}But the real truth is
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.94,0:45:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿諾太專注于 在接待員身上找意義\N{\fs14}Arnold was so focused on finding meaning in the hosts
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.61,0:45:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他沒有生存的能力\N{\fs14}he didn't have what it took to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.74,0:45:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你也沒有\N{\fs14}Looks like you don't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.25,0:46:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在明白這一切的走向了嗎 \N{\fs14}Do you understand now where all this is going?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.67,0:46:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了\N{\fs14}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.55,0:46:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得你能拯救他們嗎 \N{\fs14}Do you think you can save them?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.18,0:46:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看見一條道路\N{\fs14}I've seen a path.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.68,0:46:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看見結局了嗎 \N{\fs14}Have you seen how it ends?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.85,0:46:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對\N{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.23,0:46:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要給這世界 \N{\fs14}I'm going to give this world
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.90,0:46:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們要求已久的意義\N{\fs14}the meaning they've been asking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.24,0:46:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音調序列處理中\N{\fs14}<i>Tone sequence processing.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.98,0:46:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}＂音量警告＂
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.70,0:46:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一場游戲\N{\fs14}One last game.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.12,0:46:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音調啟動\N{\fs14}<i>Tone initiating.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.96,0:46:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接待員 人類\N{\fs14}Host, human.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.54,0:46:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一個男人 女人和小孩\N{\fs14}Every man, woman and child
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.92,0:46:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰到一個人也不剩\N{\fs14}fighting until no one remains
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.92,0:46:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了蟑螂\N{\fs14}but the cockroaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.55,0:46:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得你能拯救他們嗎 \N{\fs14}Do you think you can save them?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.48,0:46:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看見一條道路\N{\fs14}I've seen a path.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.98,0:47:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看見結局了嗎 \N{\fs14}Have you seen how it ends?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.86,0:47:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對\N{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.78,0:47:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在每個可能性中\N{\fs14}In every scenario...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.45,0:47:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都會死\N{\fs14}I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.29,0:47:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們終于要活出最高的潛能\N{\fs14}We're finally living up to our full potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.75,0:47:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜你要錯過了\N{\fs14}It's a shame you're gonna miss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.12,0:48:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得融入群眾\N{\fs14}We need to blend in.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.00,0:48:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的囚衣太顯眼\N{\fs14}Your prison garb isn't helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.89,0:48:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十元跟你買你的大衣\N{\fs14}Hey, I'll give you 50 for your coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.15,0:48:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎么回事 \N{\fs14}What the fuck was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.92,0:48:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計劃不變 我們繼續走\N{\fs14}Plan stays the same. Let's keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.10,0:48:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 \N{\fs14}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.60,0:49:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下來 停止\N{\fs14}Put that down. Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.10,0:49:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他看不見你 \N{\fs14}He can't see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.81,0:49:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們都一樣\N{\fs14}None of them can.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.31,0:49:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什么  \N{\fs14}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.15,0:49:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要怎么讓他們停止 \N{\fs14}How can I make them stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.27,0:49:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒辦法 你的力量被音調壓過了\N{\fs14}You can't. Your powers are being overridden by the tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.13,0:49:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走\N{\fs14}I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.42,0:49:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走 這里\N{\fs14}Let's go. This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.43,0:49:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里 快來\N{\fs14}This way. Come on.
